<div class='note'>
<h4>Update operators:</h4>
<ul>
<li><code>$inc</code> - increment value by given number
<li><code>$set</code> - set new value
<li><code>$unset</code> - unset key
</ul>
<ul>
<li><code>$push</code> - append item to array
<li><code>$pushAll</code> - append more items to array
<li><code>$addToSet</code> - add item to set (duplicates are not inserted)
<li><code>$pop</code> - remove last (1) or first (-1) item from array
<li><code>$pull</code> - remove all occurences of given value from array
<li><code>$pullAll</code> - remove all occurences of all given values from array
</ul>
</div>

